<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> her lantrichter, uns hat fürgelegt Hans
                        Tucher, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>lieb<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan>, wie daz <expan cert="unknown">C.</expan>
                        Teͣttel von Elhenbach den <expan cert="unknown">C.</expan> Wernher von
                        Reichelswangk, seinen armman, für euch auf das
                            <expan>lantger<ex>iht</ex></expan> geladen hab ümb sprüch, die er czu im
                                <expan>czuhab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> main, die doch weder grunt noch
                        podem anrüren. <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz ir den
                                <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> klager daran weysen wollet, das er
                        von der klag lasse, das <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc. Und het er
                                <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> czu <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan>, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urgers</ex></expan>
<expan>armman<ex>n</ex></expan>, icht <expan>czespr<ex>echen</ex></expan>,
                                <expan>dar<ex>umb</ex></expan> wil im
                            <expan>ders<ex>elbe</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> von <expan>demselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>seine</expan>
<expan>armman<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>unv<ex>er</ex>czog<ex>en</ex></expan> etc.</ab>
